Expected statistics output for `ls /tmp`:
```
syscall              calls     errors     usecs/total    %time
--------------------  ----------  ----------  ---------------  --------
mmap                      12           0            423   38.71%
openat                     8           1            312   28.53%
read                      14           0            198   18.11%
